name: DeXe (Old)
description: DeXe Protocol is a decentralized suite of permissionless tools for managing assets, products, and communities governed by $DEXE holders within DeXe Protocol DAO. It offers a no-code environment on blockchain for launching DAOs, tokens, and fundraises; AI-powered automation for decision-making; on/off-chain in a seamless space; account abstraction acting as a DAO, multi-sig or single party with numerous features for managing assets and payouts, and(or) communities.
